<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The words “under this subchapter” are added to preserve the original grant of power in the Act of <date date="1916-09-07">Sept. 7, 1916</date>.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Administration of this subchapter was transferred to the Secretary of Labor by section 1 of 1950 Reorg. Plan No. 19, <ref href="/us/stat/64/1271">64 Stat. 1271</ref> (see section 8145).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Standard changes are made to conform with the definitions applicable and the style of this title as outlined in the preface to the report.</p>
